## Shipped fixes

### Tier B modes (step 7)

**`jelly-tiles`** (index 10)
- ~15% of cells have jelly overlay (`JELLY_TILES_RATIO`)
- Goal: clear all jelly — removed when that cell is part of a match
- Candy swaps normally; green border overlay in UI

**`stone-blocks`** (index 11)
- ~12% of cells are stones (`STONE_BLOCKS_RATIO`); 1 adjacent match breaks each
- Goal: destroy all stones; blocks selection like frozen tiles
- Gray 🪨 overlay UI

Only appear in pools for **level 4+** (`getActivePool`).

**Files:** `types/index.ts`, `constants/game.ts`, `useCandyBreak.ts`, `App.tsx`, `i18n/*`

### Level-gated active pool (step 6)

Subset shuffle per level via `getActivePool` + `sampleStageOrder`. **Files:** `game.ts`, `useCandyBreak.ts`

### Random mode order per level (step 5)

`stageOrder` / `stageSlot`, derived `shapeIndex`, save migration. **Files:** `useCandyBreak.ts`

### Bomb / lightning flash

`bombActivating` — **Files:** `useCandyBreak.ts`, `App.tsx`

### Immediate goal update

`computeGoalAfterSteps` per cascade step — **Files:** `useCandyBreak.ts`

### Game Over overlay

Dim + card; tap to retry — **Files:** `App.tsx`

### Locked-tiles touch

Frozen cells use `Pressable` — **Files:** `App.tsx`, `useCandyBreak.ts`

## Play styles (current — 12 modes)

| Idx | Style | Goal | Pool | Notes |
|-----|-------|------|------|-------|
| 0 | `classic` | Clear N candies | Core | Bomb at 60% moves |
| 1 | `color-target` | Clear N of target color | Core | Random target |
| 2 | `locked-tiles` | Thaw all frozen | Core | 2 adjacent hits |
| 3 | `multiplier-rush` | Score threshold | Advanced | Combo multiplier max 8× |
| 4 | `bomb-storm` | Clear N candies | Core | Bomb respawns |
| 5 | `timer-attack` | Clear N candies | Mid | 90s countdown |
| 6 | `order-collect` | Colors in sequence | Advanced | Red/Blue/Gold queue |
| 7 | `combo-goal` | N cascade steps | Advanced | Step 2+ only |
| 8 | `move-saver` | Clear N candies | Mid | Cascade refunds moves |
| 9 | `pure-match` | Clear N candies | Mid | No specials |
| 10 | `jelly-tiles` | Clear all jelly | **Tier B** | Match on jelly cell |
| 11 | `stone-blocks` | Break all stones | **Tier B** | 1 adjacent hit |

